To send a package:
1 - Expand the package.
2 - Click the 'Send' button. Note that the 'Send' button will be disabled if you have not changed any documents.
3 - Select the people that you want to send to. People that have already seen earlier versions of this package are listed.
4 - If you want to send to a new person, type the person's name in the text box. As you type, a menu may appear making suggestions. You can select a name from the list to save you typing the whole name. You can add more than one person by separating the names with commas.
5 - Press the 'Send' button.

<p>Sometimes it is useful to attach a note when you send the package. Before sending the package, click the 'More Actions' button and select 'Edit Note'. Alternatively, click on the Working Version icon.